<s> Len (and others) Please dont dismiss the MathML work too lightly.  </s>
<s> We agonized over the trade-offs between semantic and presentational markup and I persoanlly believe that the MathML specification does an outstanding job of addressing both camps.  </s>
<s> There are quirks like phantom present in there as Chris pointed out, but these were also left in because they were felt to be essential for certain presentations.  </s>
